&lt;p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"&gt;Additional visualizers help to&lt;span style=" font-weight:700;"&gt; see the effect&lt;/span&gt; of processing&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text>
		<arrow id="8" start="(611.0, 246.09090909090912)" end="(611.9090909090909, 187.0)" fill="#c1272d" />
