&lt;p style=" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"&gt;This waterfall &lt;span style=" font-weight:700;"&gt;trimes &lt;/span&gt;the patch according to the bounding box  &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text>
		<arrow id="11" start="(246.66666666666669, 599.0909090909091)" end="(247.57575757575756, 540.0)" fill="#c1272d" />
